Aerozep.name: エアロゼップ
Aerozep.description: A modern-day cargo blimp. Requires a minimum of two rooms. The price is for each room below deck.

AV-4 Multipurpose Aerodyne.name: AV-4 多用途エアロダイン
AV-4 Multipurpose Aerodyne.description: A multipurpose aircraft capable of quick insertion thanks to vertical thrusters. Used commonly by Trauma Teams.

AV-9 Super Aerodyne.name: AV-9 スーパー・エアロダイン
AV-9 Super Aerodyne.description: A highly advanced AV with limited seats. Can travel up to 300 miles per hour.

Cabin Cruiser.name: キャビンクルーザー
Cabin Cruiser.description: A very fast speedboat. Requires a minimum of two rooms. The price is for each room below deck.

Compact Groundcar.name: 小型地上車
Compact Groundcar.description: A CHOOH2-powered groundcar. Very common with a few dozen manufacturers producing similar models.

Helicopter.name: ヘリコプター
Helicopter.description: A four-seater helicopter capable of high speeds and long flights.

High Performance Groundcar.name: 高性能地上車
High Performance Groundcar.description: A specialised groundcar designed for sports performance.

Jetski.name: ジェットスキー
Jetski.description: A common CHOOH2-powered jetski that can seat two people.

Roadbike.name: オートバイ
Roadbike.description: A common CHOOH2-powered roadbike seen during the time of the Red.

Super Groundcar.name: スーパーカー
Super Groundcar.description: An expensive, exotic CHOOH2 powered sportscar. It is capable of very high speeds.

Superbike.name: スーパーバイク
Superbike.description: A beefed-up version of a roadbike, capable of very high speeds.

Yacht.name: ヨット
Yacht.description: A luxury speedboat. Requires a minimum of two rooms. The price is for each room below or above deck.
